status`, `list`, `logs`, `stop`."," - **`cloched`** (Daemon) — Long-running. Manages container lifecycle, collects status, persists state. Executes host workflows (`host.cloche`) step by step on the host machine, dispatching container workflow runs as needed."," - **`cloche-agent`** (In-Container) — Autonomous. Parses workflow DSL, walks the graph, executes steps, streams status back to daemon. Runs to completion without human intervention."," "]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
